[2026-03-04 14:38:05] [parsed] Write: {'file_path': 'D:\\Claude\\PullRequest\\.claude\\skills\\yt-dlp-helper\\skill.md', 'content': '---\nname: yt-dlp-helper\ndescription: 浣跨敤 yt-dlp 浠庢暟鍗冧釜缃戠珯涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2戝拰闊抽\udca2慭nversion: 1.0.0\nauthor: Claude Code\n---\n\n# yt-dlp-helper Skill\n\n鏈\udcac skill 鎻愪緵浣跨敤 yt-dlp 浠庡悇绉嶇綉绔欎笅杞借\udca7嗛\udca2戝拰闊抽\udca2戠殑甯\udcae鍔┿\udc80俓n\n## 鍔熻兘姒傝堪\n\nyt-dlp 鏄\udcaf涓\udc80涓\udcaa鍔熻兘寮哄ぇ鐨勫懡浠よ\udca1屽伐鍏凤紝鏀\udcaf鎸佷粠 YouTube銆丅ilibili銆乀witch 绛夋暟鍗冧釜缃戠珯涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2戝拰闊抽\udca2戙\udc80俓n\n### 涓昏\udca6佽兘鍔沑n\n1. **涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2\udc91** - 浠庢敮鎸佺殑缃戠珯涓嬭浇鍗曚釜鎴栨壒閲忚\udca7嗛\udca2慭n2. **鎻愬彇闊抽\udca2\udc91** - 浠庤\udca7嗛\udca2戜腑鎻愬彇闊抽\udca2戝苟杞\udcac鎹\udca2涓\udcba MP3銆丮4A 绛夋牸寮廫n3. **閫夋嫨鏍煎紡** - 閫夋嫨鐗瑰畾鍒嗚鲸鐜囥\udc80佺爜鐜囨垨鏍煎紡鐨勮\udca7嗛\udca2慭n4. **涓嬭浇瀛楀箷** - 鑷\udcaa鍔ㄤ笅杞芥垨宓屽叆瀛楀箷\n5. **涓嬭浇鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛\udca8** - 涓嬭浇鏁翠釜鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛ㄦ垨棰戦亾\n6. **鍏冩暟鎹\udcae宓屽叆** - 宓屽叆灏侀潰銆佹爣棰樸\udc80佽壓鏈\udcaf瀹剁瓑鍏冩暟鎹甛n\n## 甯哥敤鍛戒护绀轰緥\n\n### 鍩虹\udca1\udc80涓嬭浇\n\n```bash\n# 涓嬭浇鍗曚釜瑙嗛\udca2戯紙鏈\udc80浣崇敾璐\udca8锛塡nyt-dlp "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2戝苟鎸囧畾淇濆瓨鐩\udcae褰昞nyt-dlp -o "downloads/%(title)s.%(ext)s" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛╘nyt-dlp "鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛\udca8 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛ㄤ腑鐨勬寚瀹氳寖鍥碶nyt-dlp --playlist-items 1-10 "鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛\udca8 URL"\n```\n\n### 闊抽\udca2戞彁鍙朶n\n```bash\n# 鎻愬彇闊抽\udca2戜负 MP3 鏍煎紡\nyt-dlp -x --audio-format mp3 "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 鎻愬彇闊抽\udca2戜负 M4A 鏍煎紡锛堥\udc80傚悎 Apple 璁惧\udca4囷級\nyt-dlp -x --audio-format m4a "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 鎻愬彇闊抽\udca2戝苟宓屽叆鍏冩暟鎹甛nyt-dlp -x --audio-format mp3 --embed-thumbnail --add-metadata "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n```\n\n### 鏍煎紡閫夋嫨\n\n```bash\n# 涓嬭浇鏈\udc80浣崇敾璐\udca8锛堣\udca7嗛\udca2\udc91 + 闊抽\udca2戝悎骞讹級\nyt-dlp -f "bestvideo+bestaudio/best" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇 1080p 瑙嗛\udca2慭nyt-dlp -f "bestvideo[height<=1080]+bestaudio/best[height<=1080]" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇 4K 瑙嗛\udca2慭nyt-dlp -f "bestvideo[height<=2160]+bestaudio/best[height<=2160]" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 浠呬笅杞借\udca7嗛\udca2戯紙涓嶅惈闊抽\udca2戯級\nyt-dlp -f "bestvideo" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 浠呬笅杞介煶棰戞祦\nyt-dlp -f "bestaudio" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n```\n\n### 瀛楀箷澶勭悊\n\n```bash\n# 涓嬭浇鑷\udcaa鍔ㄧ敓鎴愮殑瀛楀箷\nyt-dlp --write-sub --write-auto-sub "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 涓嬭浇鎸囧畾璇\udcad瑷\udc80鐨勫瓧骞曪紙涓\udcad鏂囷級\nyt-dlp --write-sub --sub-lang zh-Hans "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 灏嗗瓧骞曞祵鍏ヨ\udca7嗛\udca2戞枃浠禱nyt-dlp --embed-subs "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n```\n\n### 楂樼骇鍔熻兘\n\n```bash\n# 涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2戜俊鎭\udcaf锛堜笉涓嬭浇瑙嗛\udca2戞湰韬\udcab锛塡nyt-dlp --dump-json "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 鍒楀嚭鎵\udc80鏈夊彲鐢ㄦ牸寮廫nyt-dlp --formats "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 浠庢枃浠惰\udcaf诲彇 URL 鍒楄〃鎵归噺涓嬭浇\nyt-dlp -a urls.txt\n\n# 闄愬埗涓嬭浇閫熷害锛堥伩鍏嶅甫瀹藉崰鐢ㄨ繃楂橈級\nyt-dlp --limit-rate 500K "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n\n# 鏂\udcad鐐圭画浼燶nyt-dlp --continue "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n```\n\n## 鏀\udcaf鎸佺殑缃戠珯锛堥儴鍒嗭級\n\n- YouTube (youtube.com)\n- Bilibili (bilibili.com)\n- Twitch (twitch.tv)\n- Twitter/X (twitter.com, x.com)\n- Instagram (instagram.com)\n- TikTok (tiktok.com)\n- Vimeo (vimeo.com)\n- Dailymotion (dailymotion.com)\n- 缃戞槗浜戦煶涔\udc90 (music.163.com)\n- QQ 闊充箰 (y.qq.com)\n- 浠ュ強鏇村\udca4\udc9a 1800+ 涓\udcaa缃戠珯\n\n## 瀹夎\udca3\udc85 yt-dlp\n\n### Windows\n\n```bash\n# 浣跨敤 pip 瀹夎\udca3匼npip install yt-dlp\n\n# 浣跨敤 winget 瀹夎\udca3匼nwinget install yt-dlp\n\n# 浣跨敤 chocolatey 瀹夎\udca3匼nchoco install yt-dlp\n```\n\n### macOS\n\n```bash\n# 浣跨敤 Homebrew 瀹夎\udca3匼nbrew install yt-dlp\n\n# 浣跨敤 pip 瀹夎\udca3匼npip install yt-dlp\n```\n\n### Linux\n\n```bash\n# 浣跨敤 pip 瀹夎\udca3匼npip install yt-dlp\n\n# Ubuntu/Debian (浣跨敤瀹樻柟 PPA)\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:yt-dlp/stable\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install yt-dlp\n```\n\n## 渚濊禆椤筡n\n鏌愪簺鍔熻兘闇\udc80瑕侀\udca2濆\udca4栧畨瑁咃細\n\n```bash\n# 闊抽\udca2戝\udca4勭悊锛堟牸寮忚浆鎹\udca2銆佹彁鍙栵級\npip install ffmpeg-python\n\n# 鎴栬\udc80呯郴缁熷畨瑁匼n# Windows: winget install ffmpeg\n# macOS: brew install ffmpeg\n# Linux: sudo apt install ffmpeg\n```\n\n## 浣跨敤鎶\udc80宸\udca7\n\n1. **浣跨敤 Cookie 涓嬭浇浼氬憳鍐呭\udcae\udcb9**\n   ```bash\n   yt-dlp --cookies-from-browser chrome "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n   ```\n\n2. **浠ｇ悊璁剧疆**\n   ```bash\n   yt-dlp --proxy "http://127.0.0.1:7890" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n   ```\n\n3. **骞跺彂涓嬭浇鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛\udca8**\n   ```bash\n   yt-dlp --concurrent-fragments 5 "鎾\udcad鏀惧垪琛\udca8 URL"\n   ```\n\n4. **杈撳嚭妯℃澘鑷\udcaa瀹氫箟**\n   ```bash\n   yt-dlp -o "%(uploader)s/%(upload_date)s_%(title)s.%(ext)s" "瑙嗛\udca2\udc91 URL"\n   ```\n\n## 娉ㄦ剰浜嬮」\n\n- 璇烽伒瀹堝悇缃戠珯鐨勬湇鍔℃潯娆惧拰鐗堟潈瑙勫畾\n- 浠呬笅杞界敤浜庝釜浜哄\udcad︿範銆佺爺绌剁殑鍐呭\udcae筡n- 涓嶈\udca6佺敤浜庡晢涓氱洰鐨勬垨閲嶆柊鍒嗗彂鍙楃増鏉冧繚鎶ょ殑鍐呭\udcae筡n'}
